비비에 러브 스토리♥️

로저비비에가 이야기하는 사랑에 대한 가치를, 브랜드 앰버서더로 수년간 활동 중인 민아씨가 직접 자신만의 시각과 감성으로 해석해 기획부터, 연출, 편집, 연기까지 모든 과정을 이끌어낸 영상 ‘비비에 러브 스토리(A Vivier Love Story)’를 공개합니다!👏👏

약 4개월간 시놉시스를 직접 구성하고 로케이션 헌팅, 배우 캐스팅, 소품 및 스타일링, 음악 선곡, 편집 등 하나하나 열성적으로 준비하고✔️ 모든 스태프들과 세심하게 소통하며 자신이 담고 싶은 이야기를 담아낸 민아씨💛

ROGER VIVIER
⠀
@RogerVivier
@GherardoFelloni
@Illusomina
⠀
로저 비비에의 앰버서더인 배우 신민아가 브랜드를 위해 기획부터 연출, 연기 등 모든 과정을 이끈 영상 ‘A Vivier Love Story – 비비에 러브 스토리’를 공개합니다. 이번 영상은 로저 비비에가 이야기하는 사랑에 대한 가치를 신민아가 본인만의 시각과 감성으로 재해석한 것이 특징인데요. 여기에 로저 비비에의 크리에이티브 디렉터 게라르도 펠로니와 직접 소통하며 상상력을 더했습니다. 로저 비비에의 2020 F/W 컬렉션 키 아이템들과 함께 과거와 현재, 서울과 파리, 할머니와 손녀 등 대비되는 요소들의 아름다운 하모니를 이룬 완성도 높은 이번 영상은 8월 7일 로저 비비에 웹사이트를 통해 공개됩니다. 또한 준비 과정과 촬영 현장에서 디렉터이자 배우로서의 열정과 노력이 담긴 신민아의 모습 그리고 그녀의 코멘터리가 포함된 메이킹 영상은 8월 14일에 공개될 예정입니다.
⠀

경주 / Gyeongju (2014)
Directed by Zhang Lu

Daegu 7 am
Professor Choi-hyun impulsively  decides to visit Gyeongju one day thinking about Chun-hwa, who he met seven years ago.

11 am
The owner of the beautiful Arison teahouse , yun-hee, mistook Choi-hyun as a pervert because he was interested in an obscene painting that used to be on display. 

SinGyeongju station  2pm 
Choi-hyun meets up with an ex girlfriend but is disappointed that she only has a couple of hours to spare until she has to return to Seoul. 

Bomun Lake 5pm
After his ex-girlfriend leaves, Choi-hyun walks alone past Bomun Lake and heads back to Arison teahouse where he again meets Yun-hee. There they drink tea and talk some more.

Gathering 7pm
Yun-hee invites Choi-hyun for drinks with some friends and gradually becomes curious about him. 

Karaoke 11pm 
After drinks  Choi-hyun and Yun-hee visit the an ancient tombs and admire the view of dawn in down town Gyeongju. There Choi-hyun grows more attached to Yun-hee.

Yun-hee's house 1am

Yun-hee let's Choi-hyun stay at her house where they talk more about past relationships and their feelings. Yet, there is a strange air between them....

Gyeongju is  a very calming and peaceful film. Gentle wind blows through grass,  hypnotising sounds of Cicadas fill the air. The music is minimalist and the film just feels very Korean in general. This is quite interesting since the director was born in China. There much going on here in regards to history and I was absorbed right through to the end.

9월 가장 강렬하고 아름다운 미스터리 스릴러의 탄생을 예고한 영화 <디바>가 티저 예고편을 공개했다.
SYNOPSIS
두려움의 높이, 10미터 다이빙대의 끝에서
아름답게 낙하하다
전 세계가 주목하는 다이빙계의 디바 ‘이영’은
어느 날 동료이자 절친 ‘수진’과 함께 교통사고를 당한다.
사고 후 실종된 ‘수진’을 향한 ‘이영’의 애틋함과 달리
동료들은 ‘수진’에 대해 의문스러운 말들을 쏟아내고,
혼란스러운 와중에도 ‘이영’은 완벽한 실력을 되찾아야만 한다.
결국 최고를 지키고자 하는 강렬한 욕망과 
오랜 시간 친구로 지내왔던 ‘수진’이 자기가 알던 모습이 아닐지도 모른다는 두려움은 
‘이영’을 점점 광기로 몰아넣는데…

알 수 없는 깊이의 두려움 속으로 빠져들다

우아한 쉐잎의 실루엣이 단연 돋보이는 랩원피스입니다.
양쪽 숄더 라인에 덧대어진 러플과
그 아래로 연결된 또 다른 러플 사이로 살갗이 살짝
내비치는 형태의 디자인이 매력적인 원피스입니다.
피부에 닿는 감촉이 톡톡하고 탄탄한 조직감으로

경주 / Gyeongju (2014)
Directed by Zhang Lu

Daegu 7 am
Professor Choi-hyun impulsively  decides to visit Gyeongju one day thinking about Chun-hwa, who he met seven years ago.

11 am
The owner of the beautiful Arison teahouse , yun-hee, mistook Choi-hyun as a pervert because he was interested in an obscene painting that used to be on display. 

SinGyeongju station  2pm 
Choi-hyun meets up with an ex girlfriend but is disappointed that she only has a couple of hours to spare until she has to return to Seoul. 

Bomun Lake 5pm
After his ex-girlfriend leaves, Choi-hyun walks alone past Bomun Lake and heads back to Arison teahouse where he again meets Yun-hee. There they drink tea and talk some more.

Gathering 7pm
Yun-hee invites Choi-hyun for drinks with some friends and gradually becomes curious about him. 

Karaoke 11pm 
After drinks  Choi-hyun and Yun-hee visit the an ancient tombs and admire the view of dawn in down town Gyeongju. There Choi-hyun grows more attached to Yun-hee.

Yun-hee's house 1am

Yun-hee let's Choi-hyun stay at her house where they talk more about past relationships and their feelings. Yet, there is a strange air between them....

Gyeongju is  a very calming and peaceful film. Gentle wind blows through grass,  hypnotising sounds of Cicadas fill the air. The music is minimalist and the film just feels very Korean in general. This is quite interesting since the director was born in China. There much going on here in regards to history and I was absorbed right through to the end.

경주 / Gyeongju (2014)
Directed by Zhang Lu

Daegu 7 am
Professor Choi-hyun impulsively  decides to visit Gyeongju one day thinking about Chun-hwa, who he met seven years ago.

11 am
The owner of the beautiful Arison teahouse , yun-hee, mistook Choi-hyun as a pervert because he was interested in an obscene painting that used to be on display. 

SinGyeongju station  2pm 
Choi-hyun meets up with an ex girlfriend but is disappointed that she only has a couple of hours to spare until she has to return to Seoul. 

Bomun Lake 5pm
After his ex-girlfriend leaves, Choi-hyun walks alone past Bomun Lake and heads back to Arison teahouse where he again meets Yun-hee. There they drink tea and talk some more.

Gathering 7pm
Yun-hee invites Choi-hyun for drinks with some friends and gradually becomes curious about him. 

Karaoke 11pm 
After drinks  Choi-hyun and Yun-hee visit the an ancient tombs and admire the view of dawn in down town Gyeongju. There Choi-hyun grows more attached to Yun-hee.

Yun-hee's house 1am

Yun-hee let's Choi-hyun stay at her house where they talk more about past relationships and their feelings. Yet, there is a strange air between them....

Gyeongju is  a very calming and peaceful film. Gentle wind blows through grass,  hypnotising sounds of Cicadas fill the air. The music is minimalist and the film just feels very Korean in general. This is quite interesting since the director was born in China. There much going on here in regards to history and I was absorbed right through to the end.

👠로저 비비에의 ‘비비에 러브 스토리(A Vivier Love Story)’ 메종 앰버서더 신민아가 디렉팅한 영상 공개👠

로저 비비에(@rogervivier)가 이야기하는 사랑에 대한 가치를 앰버서더 신민아(@illusomina) 본인만의 시각과 감성으로 해석하여 영상으로 선보입니다! 완성도 있는 이번 영상은 로저 비비에의 2020 가을/겨울 컬렉션 키 아이템들과 함께 과거와 현재, 서울과 파리, 할머니와 손녀 등 대비되는 요소들의 아름다운 하모니를 보여주는데요,

따뜻한 햇살이 들어오는 거실에서 시작되는 이 영상은 나른한 오후 할머니가 꾸벅 조는 틈을 타 할머니 방에 몰래 들어간 손녀가 서랍장 속에서 로저 비비에 박스를 발견하게 되는데요, 프렌치 럭셔리 메종 로저 비비에와 앰버서더 신민아의 독보적 관계를 보여준 이번 프로젝트는 특히 브랜드의 앰버서더 신민아가 아티스트로서 브랜드에 대한 깊은 이해와 사랑을 진솔하게 영상으로 표현했다는 점에서 의미가 있지요♥️

경주 / Gyeongju (2014)
Directed by Zhang Lu

Daegu 7 am
Professor Choi-hyun impulsively  decides to visit Gyeongju one day thinking about Chun-hwa, who he met seven years ago.

11 am
The owner of the beautiful Arison teahouse , yun-hee, mistook Choi-hyun as a pervert because he was interested in an obscene painting that used to be on display. 

SinGyeongju station  2pm 
Choi-hyun meets up with an ex girlfriend but is disappointed that she only has a couple of hours to spare until she has to return to Seoul. 

Bomun Lake 5pm
After his ex-girlfriend leaves, Choi-hyun walks alone past Bomun Lake and heads back to Arison teahouse where he again meets Yun-hee. There they drink tea and talk some more.

Gathering 7pm
Yun-hee invites Choi-hyun for drinks with some friends and gradually becomes curious about him. 

Karaoke 11pm 
After drinks  Choi-hyun and Yun-hee visit the an ancient tombs and admire the view of dawn in down town Gyeongju. There Choi-hyun grows more attached to Yun-hee.

Yun-hee's house 1am

Yun-hee let's Choi-hyun stay at her house where they talk more about past relationships and their feelings. Yet, there is a strange air between them....

Gyeongju is  a very calming and peaceful film. Gentle wind blows through grass,  hypnotising sounds of Cicadas fill the air. The music is minimalist and the film just feels very Korean in general. This is quite interesting since the director was born in China. There much going on here in regards to history and I was absorbed right through to the end.

🎉9월 개봉! <디바> 티저 예고편 전격 공개!🎉

✔️ 이변 없이 금메달을 손에 넣은 ‘이영’과 노력에 비해 항상 그보다 뒤쳐지는 절친 ‘수진’을 둘러싼 미묘한 간극은 팽팽한 긴장감을 선사한다. 뿐만 아니라 이후 두 사람에게 일어난 의문의 사고로 ‘이영’이 몰랐던 ‘수진’의 모습이 서서히 드러나면서 광기와 욕망에 둘러싸인 채 서서히 망가져 가는 ‘이영’의 모습은 신민아의 역대급 연기 변신을 예고해 이목을 집중시킨다. 

✔️ 이처럼 완전히 새로운 소재의 미스터리 스릴러 탄생을 예고한 <디바> 티저 예고편은 과연 이 균열의 끝에서 ‘이영’과 ‘수진’이 어떤 비극을 맞이하게 될지 궁금증을 증폭시킨다. 실제 <디바>를 위해 고소공포증까지 극복한 각고의 노력으로 촬영에 임했다는 신민아와 이유영은 <디바>를 통해 인생 캐릭터 갱신은 물론이고, 배우로서의 새로운 모습으로 또 한번 연기 인생의 정점에 서게 될 예정이다. 

✔️ “나한테 네 자리 뺏길까 봐 무서워서 그래?”
다이빙계의 ‘디바’, 아름다움의 이면에 숨겨져 있던 욕망과 광기!

#AVivierLOVEstory #I❤️비비에 
로저 비비에가 브랜드 앰버서더 신민아가 기획, 연출, 연기의 모든 과정을 이끈 필름 ‘비비에 러브 스토리(A Vivier Love Story)’를 공개했습니다. 따뜻한 햇살이 쏟아지는 거실, 할머니가 꾸벅 조는 틈을 타 할머니 방에 몰래 들어간 손녀가 서랍장 속에서 할머니의 소중한 로저 비비에 박스를 발견하고 그 안에 담겨 있던 ’아이 러브 비비에(I Love Vivier)’ 슈즈가 과거로의 시간 여행으로 이끈다는 흥미로운 스토리입니다. 신민아가 로저 비비에의 크리에이티브 디렉터 게라르도 펠로니와 직접 소통하며 상상력을 더한 환상적인 필름을 함께 감상하시죠.
@RogerVivier

Discover #RogerVivier Love story in Rogervivier.com. 
“To wear dreams on one’s feet is to begin to give a reality to one’s dreams.” – Roger Vivier

[ NEW FILM "DIVA ] 😯😍
.
"#Diva" adalah film thriller misteri tentang Lee Young (diperankan oleh #ShinMinAh), yang dijuluki "diva dunia menyelam". Setelah kecelakaan mobil, kegilaan terus merasukinya saat dia berjuang dengan kehilangan ingatan dan menghilangnya sahabatnya Soo Jin (diperankan oleh Lee Yoo Young).

Trailer dimulai dengan Lee Young pada konferensi pers setelah pertunjukan menyelam dan Dia melihat ke kerumunan untuk melihat Soo Jin, yang pergi.

Klip itu melompat ke Lee Young di rumah sakit saat dunia mengetahui tentang kecelakaan mobilnya. Berbicara dengan pelatih selamnya Kim Hyun Min (diperankan oleh Lee Kyu Hyung ), Lee Young bertanya tentang Soo Jin. Yang mengejutkan, dia mengatakan padanya bahwa mereka bersama.

Setelah mengetahui bahwa Soo Jin menghilang, Lee Young mulai merasa dihantui oleh sahabatnya. Dia teringat kembali saat mereka melihat ubur-ubur dan Soo Jin berkomentar, “Bukankah ini terlihat seperti kamu? Ini sangat boros."

Sebelum kecelakaan itu, Soo Jin mengatakan dia berencana untuk pensiun, dan Lee Young (#ShinMinAh) meminta mereka untuk berkompetisi bersama untuk terakhir kalinya. Pelatih mereka memberi tahu Lee Young, “Katakanlah kamu mengacaukan kinerja pribadi kamu. Menurutmu siapa yang akan mendapatkan kebencian? " Dia menjawab, "Saya akan melakukannya dengan baik di keduanya."

Soo Jin (#LeeYooYoung) berkomentar, “Meski hanya sekali, aku harap kamu menjadi seperti aku. Mengapa? Apakah kamu takut aku akan menggantikanmu? ” saat Lee Young merobek jurnal yang terkunci. Setelah itu, Lee Young bertanya kepada seseorang, "Sebelum kecelakaan itu, apa yang kita bicarakan?"

Dengan semakin banyaknya adegan yang menghantui, Lee Young berkomentar, "Ada Soo Jin yang tidak aku ketahui." Pelatih mereka berkomentar, "Dia pasti iri padamu." Soo Jin berkomentar, "Kamu dari semua orang harus percaya padaku."

Lee Young semakin dalam dan semakin dalam ke kegilaan, dan pelatihnya berseru, “Kamu bilang kamu berbeda darinya. Apa perbedaan antara kamu dan dia sekarang? ” Dia menjawab, "Apakah kau melihat saya sebagai Soo Jin?"

Film "Diva" akan tayang perdana September ini.

Seru nih kayaknya 🔥❤

출연: #신민아, #이유영, #이규형, #오하늬, #주석태

영화 '디바'는 '다이빙계의 디바'로 불리는 주인공이 의문의 사고를 당한 후 기억을 잃게 됩니다. 잃었던 기억을 되찾으면서 알게 되는 진실에 대한 미스터리 스릴러로 풀어냈다고 합니다. 

한국 영화에서 다이빙 선수를 소재로 다룬 적은, 제가 알기론 거의 없는데요. 소재는 참신한 거 같습니다. 더구나 '신민아'니까... 음... 아무튼, 업계에서도 참신한 기획과 탄탄한 이야기로 주목받았다고 합니다. 

'신민아'가 대한민국 최고의 다이빙 실력으로 '다이빙계 디바'로 불리는 '이영'을, '이유영'이 '이영'의 절친한 동료 선수인 '수진'을, '이규형'이 '이영'과 '수진'의 다이빙 코치를, 조금씩 얼굴을 알리고 있는 '오하늬'가 '이영'을 동경하는 다이빙 선수 '초아'를, 요즘 뜨는 악역, '주석태'가 에이전시 대표를 연기합니다.

경주 / Gyeongju (2014)
Directed by Zhang Lu

Daegu 7 am
Professor Choi-hyun impulsively  decides to visit Gyeongju one day thinking about Chun-hwa, who he met seven years ago.

11 am
The owner of the beautiful Arison teahouse , yun-hee, mistook Choi-hyun as a pervert because he was interested in an obscene painting that used to be on display. 

SinGyeongju station  2pm 
Choi-hyun meets up with an ex girlfriend but is disappointed that she only has a couple of hours to spare until she has to return to Seoul. 

Bomun Lake 5pm
After his ex-girlfriend leaves, Choi-hyun walks alone past Bomun Lake and heads back to Arison teahouse where he again meets Yun-hee. There they drink tea and talk some more.

Gathering 7pm
Yun-hee invites Choi-hyun for drinks with some friends and gradually becomes curious about him. 

Karaoke 11pm 
After drinks  Choi-hyun and Yun-hee visit the an ancient tombs and admire the view of dawn in down town Gyeongju. There Choi-hyun grows more attached to Yun-hee.

Yun-hee's house 1am

Yun-hee let's Choi-hyun stay at her house where they talk more about past relationships and their feelings. Yet, there is a strange air between them....

Gyeongju is  a very calming and peaceful film. Gentle wind blows through grass,  hypnotising sounds of Cicadas fill the air. The music is minimalist and the film just feels very Korean in general. This is quite interesting since the director was born in China. There much going on here in regards to history and I was absorbed right through to the end.

인상적인 콜라보레이션이 하나 또 나왔습니다. 
바로 '406호 프로젝트X짙은'의 첫 번째 콜라보레이션 앨범 [Page] 인데요.
[Page]는 여태껏 살아온 수많은 날들을 책 속의 페이지에 비유하여 노래하는 트랙이라고 합니다.
여성 3인조 밴드 '406호 프로젝트'와 남성 보컬 '짙은'의 만남은 현 인디씬 팬들을 설레게 하는 조합이네요. 
기존 경쾌한 밴드사운드를 뒤로하고 차분한 감성을 담아낸 '406호 프로젝트'의 약간 다른 시도가 인상적이며, 그 위를 15년차 뮤지션 '짙은'의 매력적인 보컬이 채웁니다. 
참고로 이번 곡은 '406호 프로젝트'가 '짙은'을 위해 만들었다고 하니 그 점에 착안하여 들어보시길 추천드립니다.

경주 / Gyeongju (2014)
Directed by Zhang Lu

Daegu 7 am
Professor Choi-hyun impulsively  decides to visit Gyeongju one day thinking about Chun-hwa, who he met seven years ago.

11 am
The owner of the beautiful Arison teahouse , yun-hee, mistook Choi-hyun as a pervert because he was interested in an obscene painting that used to be on display. 

SinGyeongju station  2pm 
Choi-hyun meets up with an ex girlfriend but is disappointed that she only has a couple of hours to spare until she has to return to Seoul. 

Bomun Lake 5pm
After his ex-girlfriend leaves, Choi-hyun walks alone past Bomun Lake and heads back to Arison teahouse where he again meets Yun-hee. There they drink tea and talk some more.

Gathering 7pm
Yun-hee invites Choi-hyun for drinks with some friends and gradually becomes curious about him. 

Karaoke 11pm 
After drinks  Choi-hyun and Yun-hee visit the an ancient tombs and admire the view of dawn in down town Gyeongju. There Choi-hyun grows more attached to Yun-hee.

Yun-hee's house 1am

Yun-hee let's Choi-hyun stay at her house where they talk more about past relationships and their feelings. Yet, there is a strange air between them....

Gyeongju is  a very calming and peaceful film. Gentle wind blows through grass,  hypnotising sounds of Cicadas fill the air. The music is minimalist and the film just feels very Korean in general. This is quite interesting since the director was born in China. There much going on here in regards to history and I was absorbed right through to the end.

경주 / Gyeongju (2014)
Directed by Zhang Lu

Daegu 7 am
Professor Choi-hyun impulsively  decides to visit Gyeongju one day thinking about Chun-hwa, who he met seven years ago.

11 am
The owner of the beautiful Arison teahouse , yun-hee, mistook Choi-hyun as a pervert because he was interested in an obscene painting that used to be on display. 

SinGyeongju station  2pm 
Choi-hyun meets up with an ex girlfriend but is disappointed that she only has a couple of hours to spare until she has to return to Seoul. 

Bomun Lake 5pm
After his ex-girlfriend leaves, Choi-hyun walks alone past Bomun Lake and heads back to Arison teahouse where he again meets Yun-hee. There they drink tea and talk some more.

Gathering 7pm
Yun-hee invites Choi-hyun for drinks with some friends and gradually becomes curious about him. 

Karaoke 11pm 
After drinks  Choi-hyun and Yun-hee visit the an ancient tombs and admire the view of dawn in down town Gyeongju. There Choi-hyun grows more attached to Yun-hee.

Yun-hee's house 1am

Yun-hee let's Choi-hyun stay at her house where they talk more about past relationships and their feelings. Yet, there is a strange air between them....

Gyeongju is  a very calming and peaceful film. Gentle wind blows through grass,  hypnotising sounds of Cicadas fill the air. The music is minimalist and the film just feels very Korean in general. This is quite interesting since the director was born in China. There much going on here in regards to history and I was absorbed right through to the end.

경주 / Gyeongju (2014)
Directed by Zhang Lu

Daegu 7 am
Professor Choi-hyun impulsively  decides to visit Gyeongju one day thinking about Chun-hwa, who he met seven years ago.

11 am
The owner of the beautiful Arison teahouse , yun-hee, mistook Choi-hyun as a pervert because he was interested in an obscene painting that used to be on display. 

SinGyeongju station  2pm 
Choi-hyun meets up with an ex girlfriend but is disappointed that she only has a couple of hours to spare until she has to return to Seoul. 

Bomun Lake 5pm
After his ex-girlfriend leaves, Choi-hyun walks alone past Bomun Lake and heads back to Arison teahouse where he again meets Yun-hee. There they drink tea and talk some more.

Gathering 7pm
Yun-hee invites Choi-hyun for drinks with some friends and gradually becomes curious about him. 

Karaoke 11pm 
After drinks  Choi-hyun and Yun-hee visit the an ancient tombs and admire the view of dawn in down town Gyeongju. There Choi-hyun grows more attached to Yun-hee.

Yun-hee's house 1am

Yun-hee let's Choi-hyun stay at her house where they talk more about past relationships and their feelings. Yet, there is a strange air between them....

Gyeongju is  a very calming and peaceful film. Gentle wind blows through grass,  hypnotising sounds of Cicadas fill the air. The music is minimalist and the film just feels very Korean in general. This is quite interesting since the director was born in China. There much going on here in regards to history and I was absorbed right through to the end.
